headline: Here's How Many Shares of UnitedHealth Stock You Should Own to Get $1,000 in Yearly Dividends
summary: If you're seeking dividend income, bravo -- because dividends are hard to beat.  One dividend payer to consider is UnitedHealth Group (NYSE: UNH), with a 2.8% dividend yield.  Imagine you're seeking $1,000 in annual income from UnitedHealth stock.
